window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Fall in love with a rock star!</b> These sexy band mates and brothers have it all - heart, rhythm, soul, and are all out sexy.</p> <p>This compilation includes four full stand-alone novels containing favorite themes: surprise single dad, second chance romance, love at first sight, and best friend's little sister all wrapped up in a delicious rock star package.</p> <p>You will fall in love with the Crow Brothers - Jet, Tulsa, Rivers, Ridge - and the women that melt their alpha hearts.</p> <p>Written with emotion, you will smile, swoon, and you might even cry from the decadent journey as you rise to fame with these bad boys. Which musician will you meet first in <i>New York Times</i> and <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author S. L. Scott's best-selling series, The Crow Brothers?</p>"; 
